This is a collection of examples for Pig integration with scripting languages.

See the following JIRAs for more information:
 - Pig 0.8:
     https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-928 UDFs in scripting languages (Python support)
 - Pig 0.9:
     https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1479 Embed Pig in scripting languages (Python support)
     https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1794 Javascript support for Pig embedding and UDFs in scripting languages
